        <Parent_String>Woodland Tradition [300016671], Pre-Columbian North American styles [300016727], Pre-Columbian North American styles and periods [300016628], Pre-Columbian (American) [300016619], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
